<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - AK Cell</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/custom.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/header') %>



    <div class="p-5 text-center bg-light">
      <h1 class="text-body-emphasis display-4 fw-bold">AK CELL</h1>
      <p class="col-lg-8 mx-auto fs-4 text-muted">
        Here you can find all your social media services!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-4">
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide carousel-fade carousel-zoom" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="/images/jawaker-logo.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/free-fire.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/shahidlogo.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ticker-wrap my-4">
      <div class="ticker-text">
        اهلا بكم في AK CELL! نحن نقدم خدمات حسابات سوشيال ميديا، بطاقات هدايا، وألعاب. تابعونا للحصول على أحدث العروض والخصومات!
      </div>
    </div>

    <form class="w-50 mx-auto mt-5" id="searchForm">
      <input class="form-control form-control-lg" type="search" placeholder="Search for a service..." aria-label="Search" id="searchInput">
    </form>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Our Services</h2>
      <div class="row row-cols-2 row-cols-md-5 g-4 text-center">
        <div class="col service-card">
          <a href="/accounts" class="card-link">
            <div class="card bg-dark text-white border-0">
                <img src="images\pexels-freestocks-987586.jpg" class="card-img" alt="Accounts">
            </div>
             </a>
            <p class="mt-2 fw-bold">Accounts</p>
        
        </div>
        <div class="col service-card">
          <a href="/games" class="card-link">
            <div class="card bg-dark text-white border-0">
                <img src="images\pexels-jeshoots-com-147458-442576.jpg" class="card-img" alt="Games">
            </div>
               </a>
            <p class="mt-2 fw-bold">Games</p>
       
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="row text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4><i class="bi bi-lightning-charge-fill"></i> Fast Delivery</h4>
          <p>Your services are delivered instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill"></i> Secure Payments</h4>
          <p>We offer safe and secure payment methods.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4><i class="bi bi-headset"></i> 24/7 Support</h4>
          <p>Our team is here to help you anytime.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
   <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center p-4 mt-5">
      <div class="container">
        <p>&copy; 2025 AK Cell. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="#" class="text-white">Facebook</a> | 
          <a href="#" class="text-white">Instagram</a> | 
          <a href="#" class="text-white">WhatsApp</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>

 
      
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>